
Effective Date: 8/15/23
Last Updated: 8/15/23

1. Introduction

Welcome to "Polar: Playground," a virtual reality game developed by Lemonality and published by Lemonality Publishing (referred to as "we," "us," or "our"). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our VR game. By accessing or using "Polar: Playground," you agree to the practices described in this policy.

2. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information when you interact with our game:

a. Personal Information:

IP Address: We collect your IP address to help ensure the security of our game and to analyze user trends to improve our services.

Hardware Identifiers: We may collect hardware identifiers, such as your device's unique ID, to provide a personalized gaming experience and to troubleshoot technical issues.

PlayFab and Photon IDs: We collect PlayFab and Photon IDs to facilitate multiplayer features and maintain game progress.

b. Usage Data:

Gameplay Data: We collect information about your gameplay, including session duration, in-game actions, and interactions. This data helps us enhance gameplay and optimize user experience.

Analytics: We may gather data about your usage patterns, performance metrics, and errors. This information aids in improving game performance and identifying bugs.

3. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected information for the following purposes:

To provide and maintain our VR game's functionality and features.
To personalize your gaming experience based on hardware specifications and preferences.
To analyze user behavior and improve our game's content and features.
To enhance multiplayer features using PlayFab and Photon IDs.
To address technical issues and provide customer support.
To protect the security and integrity of our game and its users.
4. Sharing of Information

We may share your personal information under the following circumstances:

Service Providers: We may engage third-party service providers to assist us with analytics, hosting, customer support, and other functions. These providers are bound by confidentiality agreements and are only authorized to use your information for specified purposes.

Legal Compliance: We may disclose information if required by law or to protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property, as well as that of our users and the public.

5. Your Choices

You can make the following choices regarding your personal information:

Opt-Out: You can choose not to provide certain information, although this may affect your ability to use certain features of the game.

Cookies: You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.

6. Security

We take appropriate measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.

7. Updates to Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any material changes via our game or other communication channels.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [contact email address].

Thank you for choosing "Polar: Playground." We are committed to safeguarding your privacy and providing an enjoyable gaming experience.
